data.description: Existing mortgage is assumable at 3.25%. When you walk in this home you instantly feel positive energy. located in the beautiful Mountain Falls Golf Course Community that offers a clubhouse/restaurant/bar, pools, spa's, fitness facilities, jogging trails and separate parks for walking your pets and playgrounds for the kiddos.  Beautifully maintained home that offers a Spacious Living/Dining that is perfect for entertaining.  Large Primary bedroom and primary bath has separate tub and shower with dual vanity sinks and large walk in closet.  Kitchen has granite counter tops and stainless steel stove/range and built in microwave.  Ceramic flooring in kitchen, dining and bathrooms. Three additional closets that are perfect for storage.  Separate laundry room. 2 car Garage has electric opener.  Full desert landscape front and rear.  Backyard yard has partial covered patio perfect for relaxation and enjoyment. $500.00 Home Warranty to be paid by seller.
